{"tid":1744242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府根本唔知催淚彈正確成分係咩,但上網可以話你知D","createTime":"2019-11-21T15:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T05:59:19.000Z","uid":136992,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6510d884ce9a57c7ba12b45fef4ca94ac16060","tid":1744242,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:20:34.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始昨日指，警方表示「不想影響行動部署和行動能力」，認為催淚彈成分「不宜公開」。<br />\n其實呢D係公開資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/fitz.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E4%B9%8B%E5%9F%8E-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E9%95%B7%E8%B7%91%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96-f.png?fit=1024%2C535&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ffitz.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%259F%258E-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25B7%2591%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2596-f.png%3Ffit%3D1024%252C535%26ssl%3D1&h=472d674e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地睇返呢一粒<br />\n係Nonlethal technologies出既<br />\n可能係MP-6M5-CS 一發5粒CS彈<br />\n我地睇返佢公司網頁既DATA SHEET<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/pdf/NLT_Data_Sheets.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2Fpdf%2FNLT_Data_Sheets.pdf&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=92b301e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/pdf/NLT_Data_Sheets.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqLC5RK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqLC5RK.png&h=ab530bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一款TG<br />\n化學物質 Chemical Weight:94 grams<br />\n淨催淚物質Net Irritant Agent:26 grams <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyUwqTd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyUwqTd.png&h=3ab0b4dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/pdf/SDS/SDS-MP-6M5-CS.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2Fpdf%2FSDS%2FSDS-MP-6M5-CS.pdf&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=7f3df665\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/pdf/SDS/SDS-MP-6M5-CS.pdf</a><br />\n催淚彈入面化學mixture<br />\n就包括<br />\n&gt;80% [(2-chlorophenyl)methylene]malononitrile 即CS GAS<br />\n &lt;10% magnesium oxide<br />\n&lt;2% magnesium carbonate<br />\n&lt;2% potassium perchlorate<br />\n&lt;1% barium chromate<br />\n&lt;1% aluminium powder<br />\n&lt;1% nickel<br />\n&lt;1% zirconium powder<br />\n以上部分係爆炸性物質<br />\n有咩留返比kkwong解<br />\n仲有一D trade components<br />\n例如致癌的lead styphnate, 有毒既potassium nitrate<br />\n<br />\n咁好簡單，點解政府根本唔知正確成分係咩<br />\n佢大大隻字寫住 TG彈入面既正確成份比率<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係商業秘密</span></span><br />\n<br />\n身為一個護士, 每次用藥打針其實都係用緊化學物質<br />\n對於病人, 護士係最後防線<br />\n佢地無醫生咁了解開藥既原因<br />\n佢地無藥劑師咁了解藥物所含既化學物質<br />\n但就係呢度最後防線, 去保障病人安全<br />\nDO NO HARM<br />\n一有懷疑對病人有害既野 一定唔做<br />\n人地既data sheet都講明<br />\n- 皮膚接觸有毒<br />\n- 吸入可致命<br />\n- 引致過敏/哮喘反應<br />\n唔識隻藥係咩, 都可以識查下drug guide, 睇下drug insert先用<br />\n我身為後輩<br />\n我建議下呢為醫護界老前輩, 返去睇清楚TG gas既guide<br />\n唔好官字兩個口,兩個都用曬黎奶共<br />\n上左位就連護士既天職都忘記左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d9f6632f55f307dcf3523ec59f4dfc3da29dce","tid":1744242,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:21:41.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"c1c3f05b9db7c2cb182f3b9bfbf89b8ade89f69a","tid":1744242,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:22:05.000Z","msg":"護士好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d18e100f110386464a52002726bd7fb4b0a0488","tid":1744242,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T